        <mxCell id="p05-c80" value="&lt;b&gt;Status.&lt;/b&gt; Communities &quot;Core&quot; is fully shipped and deployed to production — tabbed detail (Chat / Tips / Announcements / Events), rules, roles &amp;amp; moderation, join approval, community events and translation. Client + 3 Cloud Functions + firestore.rules are all live.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pattern.&lt;/b&gt; Announcements and community events fan out to members on write rather than being polled — same shape as group chat. Member lists are subcollections with their own rule blocks." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F9A825;fontSize=11;fontColor=#5D4037;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="760" width="1579" height="85" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
