        <mxCell id="p10-c94" value="&lt;b&gt;iOS pod constraint.&lt;/b&gt; Firebase 11 requires GoogleDataTransport ~&amp;gt;10. Keep ML Kit on the GoogleMLKit 9.0 generation (face 0.13.2 / image labeling 0.14.2) and mobile_scanner 7.x (Apple Vision — pulls no MLKit pod) or the Podfile will not resolve. This is verifiable from the pub-cache podspecs and the CocoaPods CDN without a Mac.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Media cost.&lt;/b&gt; Uploads are compressed server-side after write, never trusted from the client; thumbnails and transcriptions are derived assets with their own lifecycle (&lt;b&gt;cleanupDisappearingMedia&lt;/b&gt; is scheduled)." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F9A825;fontSize=11;fontColor=#5D4037;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="1352" width="1579" height="85" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
